  "body": "### What is wrong?\r\n\r\nThe same code for validating public keys can be found in both of these locations.\r\n\r\n* https://github.com/pipermerriam/py-evm/blob/master/evm/utils/address.py#L30-L33\r\n* https://github.com/pipermerriam/py-evm/blob/master/evm/utils/secp256k1.py#L22-L25\r\n\r\n### How can it be fixed\r\n\r\nExtract this code into a new validation function, `evm.validation.validate_raw_public_key`.  It should perform the following checks.\r\n\r\n* the value is of type `bytes`\r\n* the value is of length 64",
